    <string name="MainActivity_label">MAIN ACTIVITY (LAUNCHER):</string>
    <string name="MainActivity_description">
        This is the main screen. A search bar allows the user to search right away for whatever
        song, album or artist he has in mind at the moment (not implemented).
        Below appear suggestions for new, popular or recommended music to be
        found in the store. Each suggested item links to the related music-store page
        (not implemented). Each item in the category \'Recently Purchased\' links to the
        related album in the user\'s library (implemented).
    </string>

    <string name="MyLibrary_label">\'MY LIBRARY\' ACTIVITY:</string>
    <string name="MyLibrary_description">
        This tabbed activity allows to browse the user\'s music library by artist, album
        or song.
        Clicking a particular artist shows the artist\'s albums
        contained in the user\'s library.
        Clicking a particular album shows the list of album tracks.
        Clicking a particular song starts the activity PLAY SINGLE.
    </string>

    <string name="Artist_label">\'ARTIST\' ACTIVITY:</string>
    <string name="Artist_description">
        It shows the list of albums by the selected artist contained in the library.
        Clicking any of the albums shows the list of album tracks.
    </string>

    <string name="Album_label">\'ALBUM\' ACTIVITY:</string>
    <string name="Album_description">
        It shows the list of tracks contained in the selected album.
        Clicking any of the tracks starts the activity PLAY ALBUM TRACK.
    </string>

    <string name="AlbumFromArtist_label">\'ALBUM FROM ARTIST\' ACTIVITY:</string>
    <string name="AlbumFromArtist_description">
        It shows the list of tracks contained in the selected album.
        Clicking any of the tracks starts the activity PLAY ALBUM TRACK.
    </string>

    <string name="PlaySingle_label">\'PLAY SINGLE\' ACTIVITY:</string>
    <string name="PlaySingle_description">
        It provides song details and has an embedded media player (not implemented).
        Clicking the album cover, extra media-player controls appear in a toggle view.
    </string>

